# TOOLKIVT v2.2

This update introduces a major UI redesign and a new configuration system.

## What's New

- New Settings window.
- Configuration saved in `settings.ini`.
- Added Help and About sections.
- Added Windows minimize support.
- Improved interface layout.
- Better project organization.
- Various bug fixes and stability improvements.

## Fixed

- Fixed invalid key detection.
- Fixed Settings window initialization.
- Fixed configuration loading.
- Improved hotkey management.

